      "updated": 1783828554455,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Ancestry: Goblin\n- Keen Senses: Can't be surprised\n\nBackground: Wanted\n\"There's a price on your head, but\nyou have allies\"\n\nAlignment: Chaotic\naligned with destruction, ambition,\nand wickedness.\nadopts a \"survival of the fittest\"\nmentality.\n\nDeity: Shune the Vile\nwhispers arcane secrets to\nsorcerers and witches who call to\nher in the dark hours.\nschemes to displace Ord so she can\ncontrol the vast flow of magic\nherself.\n\nAllies:\n- 3 famous bard allies (TBD??)\n- Gorgoroth the snake wizard\n\nNotes:\nI have forgotten the tribe I came\nfrom. I still remember the\nbitterness of being exiled from it.\n\nWizard Talents:\n- +2 INT\n- +1 spellcasting",
      "fontSize": 21.642512077294686,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "e44gGHrk_4kgrsl2Pjah5",
      "originalText": "Ancestry: Goblin\n- Keen Senses: Can't be surprised\n\nBackground: Wanted\n\"There's a price on your head, but you have allies\"\n\nAlignment: Chaotic\naligned with destruction, ambition, and wickedness.\nadopts a \"survival of the fittest\" mentality.\n\nDeity: Shune the Vile\nwhispers arcane secrets to sorcerers and witches who call to her in the dark hours.\nschemes to displace Ord so she can control the vast flow of magic herself.\n\nAllies:\n- 3 famous bard allies (TBD??)\n- Gorgoroth the snake wizard\n\nNotes:\nI have forgotten the tribe I came from. I still remember the bitterness of being exiled from it.\n\nWizard Talents:\n- +2 INT\n- +1 spellcasting",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
