      "text": "Detect Thoughts [T2] [WAND]\nDuration: Focus\nRange: Near\n\nchoose 1 creature in Near range.\neach round learn its immediate\nthoughts. on each of its turns\nit makes a WIS check vs my last\nspellcasting check. when it\nsucceeds the spell ends, and it\nknows I was reading its mind.",
      "fontSize": 14.714285714285706,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "frhM0O14AMQwl2nL92vUw",
      "originalText": "Detect Thoughts [T2] [WAND]\nDuration: Focus\nRange: Near\n\nchoose 1 creature in Near range. each round learn its immediate thoughts. on each of its turns it makes a WIS check vs my last spellcasting check. when it succeeds the spell ends, and it knows I was reading its mind.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
